        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Improved Force Barrier</em></p>\n<p>This power massively bolsters your allies with toughness and resolve. Creatures of your choice in a 30-foot radius around you when you cast this power gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The creature sheds dim light in a 5-foot radius.</li>\n<li>The creature has advantage on all saving throws</li>\n<li>Other creatures have disadvantage on attack rolls against them.</li>\n<li>When a dark side creature hits them with a melee attack, that creature must make a Constitution saving throw or be blinded until the power ends.</li>\n</ul>",
